Felt like it was finally time to start dishing out some YWTGTHFT lore. The base idea here came from a nightmare of mine. Made my own version of the ACS bar 'cause I'm fussy like that.

For those wondering, the  class is used when the anomalous capabilities of an SCP are fluid, inconstant, and unpredictable. It embodies a state of impermanence, and containment efforts must adapt to an ever-changing set of circumstances. It was originally a theoretical object class that I thought had potential.
